{
  "page": "Pyramid of Qaggaz",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>pyramid of Qaggaz</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid\" title=\"Pyramid\">pyramid</a> found in <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>. Golden in color, it is the seat of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Qaggaz\" title=\"House of Qaggaz\">House of Qaggaz</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Qaggaz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Come, my little friends, I will show you to your new home. In <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a> you will dwell in the golden <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid\" title=\"Pyramid\">pyramid</a> of Qaggaz and dine off silver plates, but here we live simply, in the humble tents of soldiers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Nurse\" title=\"Nurse\">Nurse</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Qaggaz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 47\">Chapter 47</a>, Tyrion X.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404204542\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 228/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8648/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1316/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 378/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 805/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   13.364      1 -total\n 73.43%    9.813      2 Template:Ref\n 50.35%    6.729      2 Template:Ref/core\n 27.93%    3.733      1 Template:Quote\n 16.96%    2.267      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:39117-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404204542 and revision id 328348\n -->\n",
